<html><head><meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark"><meta charset="utf-8"></head><body><pre>{"id":3,"date":"2023-07-16T00:46:53","date_gmt":"2023-07-16T00:46:53","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/melbacg.au\/?page_id=3"},"modified":"2023-07-18T02:35:07","modified_gmt":"2023-07-18T02:35:07","slug":"privacy-policy","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/privacy-policy\/","title":{"rendered":"Privacy Policy"},"content":{"rendered":"\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\"&gt;This is the website of the Melbourne Anarchist Communist Group.&lt;\/strong&gt; &lt;br&gt;Our website address is: http:\/\/melbacg.au.&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;This privacy policy exists to meet the bureaucratic requirements of a plugin we have installed. &lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;1. Personal Information&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;Personal information includes things like names, contact details, and anything else about you that you might give us. We only collect personal information if you voluntarily provide it to us. If you don&amp;#8217;t want us to have your personal information don&amp;#8217;t give it to us.&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;2. Non-Personal Information&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;When you interact with this website, the various plugins and bits of software running on it may collect non-personal information such as your browser name, computer type, and technical details about your connection. We don&amp;#8217;t like it either, but it&amp;#8217;s basically impossible to run a website without this shit. &lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;3. Cookies&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;Our website may use cookies, which are small files stored on your computer, to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies help us remember your preferences and track website usage. You can choose to disable cookies in your web browser, but this may affect certain features of our website. Maybe install &lt;a href=\"https:\/\/www.eff.org\/pages\/privacy-badger\"&gt;Privacy Badger&lt;\/a&gt; if you give a shit about this kind of thing.&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;4. Embedded content from other websites&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;5. How we use your data&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;We use data you provide to do things like contact you, send you newsletters, and generally bring about the revolution. &lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;We try really hard not to share your data with scumbags, but lets be real, this is the internet. We use a variety of commercial services to make this website work (hosting companies, WordPress plugins, spam detection services and so on). Any number of commercial services that we use to make this website work could be up to no good, and we would be none the wiser.&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;We do our best within our limited capacities, but you need to &lt;a href=\"https:\/\/ssd.eff.org\/\"&gt;have your head screwed on&lt;\/a&gt;.&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;6. Your rights to your data&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;7. Application of this policy&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;By using this website you agree to this policy. If you do not agree to this policy, stop using this website. This policy may change without warning or notice. If you continue using this website you agree to any changed policy.&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;The Melbourne Anarchist Communist Group can be contacted at melbourneanarchistcommunist@proton.me&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;\/p&gt;\n\n\n\n&lt;p&gt;This policy was updated 17 July 2023.&lt;\/p&gt;\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"This is the website of the Melbourne Anarchist Communist Group. Our website address is: http:\/\/melbacg.au. This privacy policy exists to meet the bureaucratic \n&lt;a class=\"moretag\" href=\"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/privacy-policy\/\"&gt; [...]&lt;\/a&gt;","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1867,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","template":"","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":"","footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-3","page","type-page","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1156,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3\/revisions\/1156"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1867"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}</pre><div class="json-formatter-container"></div></body></html>